properties.flavorText: Ahhhh, fresh spring water. A favorite of Dolphins. Mage has a secret stash of this in his dojo, but refuses to let anyone near it.
Shinies. Shinies! Jar of shinies! Wait, I found one of these in my sandwich once...
A putrid-smelling but fabulous-tasting fungus. Strangely, it makes you feel like you're surrounded by trees.
A crystal that appears to be preserving some chunks of dirt inside of it.
The eye of a rockman. Gooey to the touch, but you couldn't smash it if you tried.
A pebble native to the artists of the Homlet Town. One of them must have gotten lost.
A small glob of ooze that glows in the dark.
